Re: Proof-of-work difficulty increasing

Bitcointalk

2010-07-16 14:46:12 UTC - [11]Original Post

   The proof-of-work difficulty is currently 45.38.  (see
   [12]http://www.alloscomp.com/bitcoin/calculator.php)
   Itʼs about to increase again in a few hours.  Itʼs only been 3-4 days
   since the last increase, so I expect it will increase by the max of 4
   times, or very nearly the max.  That would put it at 181.54.
   The target time between adjustments is 14 days, 14/3.5 days = 4.0 times
   increase.
